&lt;li&gt;The Anesthesiologist must be comfortable providing independent nasal intubation/TIVA to healthy pediatric dental patients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cases are Monday – Friday. We start between 5:30 and 6:00 am, and all cases end between 1:30 and 2:00 pm.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No call, no weekends, evenings, or holidays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1099 has the availability and is willing to work with us 15-20 days/month.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive 1099 salary-paid on a per case basis. Lots of opportunities for business expense write-offs!&lt;/li&gt;
