&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MD Anesthesiologist — Office-Based Pediatric Dental&lt;/strong&gt; Multiple openings across Oregon &amp;amp; Washington | Exceptional Flexibility | Real Work–Life Balance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oregon:&lt;/strong&gt; Eugene · Lake Oswego · Medford · Portland · Roseburg · Salem · Springfield &lt;strong&gt;Washington:&lt;/strong&gt; Federal Way · Pasco · Puyallup&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Ambulatory Anesthesia Care – Pacific Northwest (AAC-PNW)&lt;/strong&gt;, we deliver high-quality, office-based anesthesia across pediatric dental offices throughout the Pacific Northwest — and we&#39;re hiring across all of our markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;We&#39;re seeking an MD Anesthesiologist comfortable practicing in office-based pediatric dental settings. Our patients are healthy pediatric dental patients (primarily ASA I), with efficient cases and short sedation and recovery times. No complex pediatric cases — just thoughtful, well-run care in a calm environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Role Stands Out&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Many of our dental offices start early and finish early, with days often wrapping up by 1–2 PM. That means more time for family, personal commitments, outdoor adventures, or simply enjoying where you live. We&#39;re open to building a schedule that works for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Practice That&#39;s Growing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Our work today is 100% pediatric dental — but we&#39;re a growing business, expanding into adult dental, GI, and ENT. That means real opportunity to broaden your scope and grow alongside the practice, not just fill shifts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
