&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Healthy, low-acuity pediatric patients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Efficient, predictable workflows&lt;/li&gt;
