&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have a career.&amp;nbsp; Now &lt;em&gt;live your life,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;too.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At M2 Anesthesia, we specialize in general anesthesia for pediatric dental patients &lt;strong&gt;and&lt;/strong&gt; an excellent quality of life for our anesthesiologists.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have an immediate need for a 1.0 Anesthesiologist to service our dental clients in the South of Seattle division.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak&quot;&gt;Apply by August 15, 2024 and qualify for a 2-year retention bonus: $15,000 after the first year and $15,000 after the second year!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak&quot;&gt;Additional incentive: $30k sign-on for FT MD who can start by 11/1/24!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our patients are healthy, office-based, pediatric dental patients (ASA 0 or 1). Cases have short sedation and recovery times.&lt;strong&gt; If you are willing to perform both general anesthesia and oral surgery procedures for patients up to 20 years old - this job is for you!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Our dentists start early, which allows most days to wrap up by 1 or 2pm. This gives our anesthesiologists the opportunity to be present at their kids after school activities, make their own doctor appointments, or just enjoy the great outdoors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;M2 offers a lifestyle job at hospital-based compensation.&amp;nbsp; Pediatric certification is not required. Employment and compensation options include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible schedules – you pick the number of days and weeks you want to work each year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1099 options – minimum daily rates with incentives for over 6 cases/day&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;W2 packages – covered malpractce, health/dental/vision, 401(k) match, CME/auto allowances, 6 weeks PTO and 7 holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay close to home – we schedule you at only one office per day, within 60 minutes from your home&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sign-on bonuses, including additional incentives for anesthesiologists with an existing OR or WA license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional incentives for anesthesiologist and dental office referrals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salaries – upwards of $550K for full-time work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to be more than a number, be more engaged with patient care, and return to being part of the solution for the future of healthcare in targeting the Quadruple Aim, M2 Anesthesia IS your new work home!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

